---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with GenAIPick. Send suggestions, feedback, or just say hello."
>
  <div class="static-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="static-content">
        <h1>Contact</h1>
        
        <p>Have a question, suggestion, or just want to chat about AI tools? I'd love to hear from you.</p>
        
        <h2>What I Can Help With</h2>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Tool review requests and suggestions</li>
          <li>Corrections or updates to existing articles</li>
          <li>General questions about AI tools</li>
          <li>Collaboration opportunities</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>What I Probably Can't Help With</h2>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Personal AI implementation advice (I don't have capacity for consulting)</li>
          <li>Guest posting requests (my content stays authentic)</li>
          <li>Spam</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How to Reach Me</h2>
        
        <p>Send me an email at: <strong><a href="mailto:hello@genaipick.com">hello@genaipick.com</a></strong></p>
        
        <p>I try to respond to all legitimate messages, but I get a lot of emails. Give me a few days, and I'll get back to you.</p>
        
        <p>Thanks for reaching out!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
